     <body>
     <div type="poem">
   <head>The effects of prayer.</head>
   <l>THe Sunne by prayer</l>
   <l>did ceasse his course and staid:</l>
   <l>The hungrie Lions</l>
   <l>fawnd vpon their pray:</l>
   <l>A walled passage</l>
   <l>through the sea it made,</l>
   <l>From furious fire</l>
   <l>it banisht heate away:</l>
   <l>It shut the heauens</l>
   <l>three yeares from giuing raine,</l>
   <l>It opened heauens,</l>
   <l>and clouds powrd downe againe,</l>
</div>
